I'll sort it out.
-How?

29
00:02:02,256 --> 00:02:10,699
What're you gonna say? 'You can't stop me from talking to the boy whose father --'
-Please, Mum... He's something else too... Something much more...

30
00:02:10,699 --> 00:02:14,522
