37
00:02:36,305 --> 00:02:38,410
Hurt?

38
00:02:38,410 --> 00:02:40,540
What d'you want to say?

39
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:45,633
You think your Dad's heroism is something that hurts us?

40
00:02:45,761 --> 00:02:48,185
Doesn't it?

41
