Us?

47
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:12,208
Why?

48
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:15,395
She wants to help.

49
00:03:15,472 --> 00:03:17,352
Are you out to lunch?

50
00:03:17,352 --> 00:03:19,900
Why'd she want to help us?

51
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:22,600
Who asked for her help?

52
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,381
Me...

53
00:03:24,459 --> 00:03:28,969
What do <i>you</i> want from them?

54
00:03:31,950 --> 00:03:33,704
Mum...

55
00:03:35,467 --> 00:03:38,155
Nadir's teacher told me --

56
00:03:38,155 --> 00:03:40,024
The other day...

57
00:03:40,024 --> 00:03:42,930
That he's got a learning disability...

58
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:45,200
Probably dyslexia...

59
00:03:45,307 --> 00:03:49,860
I couldn't figure it out, so I talked to Vishal...

60
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:55,020
He said his Mum's a psychiatrist who's worked with SEND kids...

61
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:59,252
What's the big deal if I talked to him about it?

62
00:03:59,608 --> 00:04:01,714
You should've talked to me...

63
00:04:01,714 --> 00:04:04,232
You should've told me what his teacher said.

64
00:04:04,232 --> 00:04:13,900
But <i>you</i>'re looking for help in India... As if we haven't got anyone who can help here! And -- Of all the people... Did you have to ask <i>him</i>?
-Mum -- I was too troubled to think! I didn't want to trouble you!

65
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:19,607
I didn't even know if she was right about what she said...

66
00:04:21,229 --> 00:04:27,069
Could you - <i>any of you</i> - not get up my nose for a change, like, ever?

67
00:04:27,069 --> 00:04:30,336
My brother doesn't want to talk to me because of you...

68
00:04:30,336 --> 00:04:36,750
I've never stepped out of the house, but I've got no end of things to do out there!

69
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:41,727
Who d'you think we've got who can help us? But you had to create another mess!

70
00:04:41,727 --> 00:04:45,338
For Christ's sake... Just spare me! Please!

71
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:05,187
Yes, it's Mrs Brigadier Malhotra, Colonel Vijay Malhotra's mother...

72
00:05:05,724 --> 00:05:07,664
Thank you...

73
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:12,646
I thought if you could help me...

74
00:05:12,646 --> 00:05:22,267
I'd rented the place my husband got after his retirement out...

75
00:05:23,170 --> 00:05:24,875
Yeah...

76
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:28,566
The tenant doesn't want to leave...

77
00:05:28,566 --> 00:05:31,756
I'll give you all the details...

78
00:05:31,806 --> 00:05:36,886
But he's very rude... Almost threatening...

79
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:43,931
I want him out this month. Because I want to sell it right away.

80
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:47,187
Okay. Thank you.

81
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,759
Mum...

82
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:16,232
Granny's talking to someone from the Unit...

83
00:06:16,282 --> 00:06:19,077
I'm going to see them tomorrow...

84
00:06:19,077 --> 00:06:22,002
I'm sure the Army can kick them out.

85
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:24,947
They can't do nothing...

86
00:06:24,947 --> 00:06:30,388
Even the Army's powerless before the sort your Granny's rented that place to...

87
00:06:30,388 --> 00:06:33,702
Your Dad tried to stop her, but when does she listen to reason?

88
00:06:33,702 --> 00:06:42,410
It's all just... Brahmin sentiment to her... Thought it'd be nice if someone her class... From the party she's always rooting for... Could stay there... Yet here we are...

89
00:06:42,410 --> 00:06:43,975
Mum...

90
00:06:44,612 --> 00:06:47,675
They're nothing before the Army...

91
00:06:47,675 --> 00:06:52,632
I'm a hero's son... I'm sure they'd show some respect...

92
00:06:52,687 --> 00:06:54,903
'Respect'...

93
00:06:54,903 --> 00:07:02,220
There's millions like you in the billion people here... A bunch of them lose their lives every day... How many d'you think they'd respect?

94
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:07,017
Why're you so bitter?

95
00:07:07,017 --> 00:07:10,341
I'm not bitter. Just realistic.

96
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,337
Here...

97
00:07:12,652 --> 00:07:14,952
They've made an order to show cause...

98
00:07:14,952 --> 00:07:18,709
For my 'long and unexplained leave'.

99
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:23,133
They know everything...

100
00:07:23,133 --> 00:07:26,320
Well, just tell them?

101
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:30,412
I'm trying to... I'm writing my reply...

102
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:36,193
I'm the late Colonel Vijay Malhotra's widow...

103
00:07:36,193 --> 00:07:43,786
I'm sorry I couldn't attend to my duties because of my husband's sudden and unexpected demise.

104
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:49,450
The nation wants sacrifices...

105
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:51,793
Not excuses...

106
00:07:52,690 --> 00:07:57,591
That's all it asks of its people...

107
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:20,488
So...

108
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:23,534
Say something, will ya?

109
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:26,165
What?

110
00:08:26,165 --> 00:08:28,370
What is it?

111
00:08:29,690 --> 00:08:32,032
How d'you know?

112
00:08:32,032 --> 00:08:34,781
I can hear it in your voice.

113
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:38,110
I know you're troubled.

114
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:48,000
What is it this time?

115
00:08:53,210 --> 00:08:56,233
Dad shouldn't have left us...

116
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:03,384
Not like this... Not so soon...

117
00:09:03,384 --> 00:09:06,051
That's what I'm thinking too...

118
00:09:06,051 --> 00:09:08,193
We needed him here...

119
00:09:08,193 --> 00:09:12,850
Grandma's estate... The one Aunt wants a share in...

120
00:09:12,850 --> 00:09:15,315
Has been taken over by the tenants.

121
00:09:15,315 --> 00:09:16,183
What?

122
00:09:16,183 --> 00:09:22,034
Aye. We gotta do something. And do it quick. Aunt's coming in two days. No way she's gonna take this nicely.

123
00:09:22,034 --> 00:09:26,725
Why don't you talk to the Unit? They'll throw them out in a moment.

124
00:09:26,809 --> 00:09:28,821
