128
00:09:39,810 --> 00:09:45,230
Anyway, did you talk to Mum... About that... Thing?

129
00:09:49,890 --> 00:09:53,859
Grandpa's found out I talk to you.

130
00:09:55,650 --> 00:09:58,055
That why you're worried?

131
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:01,432
