00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,873
You there?

155
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:11,102
Did I stick around too long?

156
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:16,655
Did you mind it? Me saying that...

157
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:21,737
Sorry, I didn't hear you.

