00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,716
(How do I say it...?)

159
00:12:29,450 --> 00:12:31,219
Sarah...

160
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:34,812
You know, I --

161
00:12:34,812 --> 00:12:37,547
I think you're very...

162
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,626
Uh...

163
00:12:38,626 --> 00:12:40,809
A -- Actually...

164
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:43,260
What I want to say is --

165
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,399
Anyway, I'm honestly sleepy...

166
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:48,329
Gotta get some rest. Bye.

167
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:53,900
Okay, good night...

168
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:15,915
The stars and the heavens above...

