196
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,307
Amna...

197
00:16:07,307 --> 00:16:09,604
Don't worry.

198
00:16:09,890 --> 00:16:11,873
I'll do my best.

199
00:16:12,029 --> 00:16:18,042
I'll look for someone. Do something for him. Sort this out.

200
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:28,766
Who d'you think did all of this when wee Sherali fell ill?

201
00:16:28,766 --> 00:16:32,455
