211
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:40,200
I'll talk to Rabia and Ayesha...

212
00:17:40,690 --> 00:17:44,412
The doctors in the UK and the States can treat anything...

213
00:17:44,412 --> 00:17:49,524
Besides, I'm sure they'll do anything they can for their nephew...

214
00:17:49,524 --> 00:17:52,210
They'd care for him...

215
00:17:52,650 --> 00:17:53,957
Hello?

216
00:17:54,051 --> 00:17:56,089
