221
00:18:06,534 --> 00:18:09,494
Something's come up --

222
00:18:09,494 --> 00:18:12,571
Why am I not surprised?

223
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:15,982
Otherwise, why'd you think of me?

224
00:18:15,982 --> 00:18:19,379
I'm sorry but I don't have the time...

225
00:18:19,379 --> 00:18:23,781
But don't worry... I'm sure your in-laws can help...

226
00:18:36,510 --> 00:18:41,774
Why d'you want to talk to Rabia? She left us in a fit of rage!

227
00:18:41,774 --> 00:18:45,170
Who else have I got?

228
00:18:45,170 --> 00:18:49,447
Amna's brother doesn't seem to care!

229
00:18:50,201 --> 00:18:53,179
I'm sure it's the same with Rabia...

230
00:18:56,930 --> 00:18:58,630
And...

231
00:18:58,630 --> 00:19:00,822
And... Ayesha?

232
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:12,270
♪ <i>You're the stuff of...</i> ♪

